### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">وَكَذَٰلِكَ جَعَلْنَا فِى كُلِّ قَرْيَةٍ أَكَـٰبِرَ مُجْرِمِيهَا لِيَمْكُرُوا۟ فِيهَا ۖ وَمَا يَمْكُرُونَ إِلَّا بِأَنفُسِهِمْ وَمَا يَشْعُرُونَ</span>

### English

And so We have placed in every society the most wicked to conspire in it. Yet they plot only against themselves, but they fail to perceive it.